Welcome to Pega Workflow AI, the reusable pattern: intake, triage, decision, action, and feedback.

2
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:22,000
At intake, an LLM classifies and extracts key fields. At triage, a prediction scores urgency or value. At decision, real-time decisioning selects the next best action with constraints.

3
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:32,000
At action, a GenAI connector drafts the email or note. Feedback logs outcomes to improve prompts and models.

4
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:42,000
Use Process AI for predictions, Decisioning for arbitration, and GenAI connectors for bounded language tasks.

